Garifuna Settlement Day 2013

The National garifuna council of Belize, its divisions, affiliates and branches have the following events planned for your participation:

On November 19th 2013

Friday serene fries and Garifuna Drumming session sumukha café. 4 p.m. to 6:30 p.m.

Followed by 7 p.m. to 8 p.m. meeting with The Honorable Minister John Saldivar

Out- Reaching Session regarding Project advance for fiscal years 2013-2014 Djembe, Drums accompaniment are greatly needed!

On November 21st 2013 Thursday AIYEBALI & DOSOROGA Church word session Everyone is invited!

On November 22nd 2013 Friday National Garifuna council Conference Meeting and prays Brother and Sister in Christ, are invited!

On November 23rd 2013 Ceremony at La Laguna, Santa Cruz Village

At 7 a.m. flag raising to National Anthem The Morning star flag and proclamation readings ceremony at the gazebo followed by Praise and worship service.

Nguzugoro Massing at About 10a.m
